00:20:30.200 --> 00:20:32.660
And again, we built
this entire system

00:20:32.660 --> 00:20:34.350
to put a household
through it, and it's

00:20:34.350 --> 00:20:36.120
very thoughtfully
in a certain order.

00:20:36.120 --> 00:20:37.200
So first, we've gotta
get you organized,

00:20:37.200 --> 00:20:38.699
we gotta know what
your numbers are,

00:20:38.699 --> 00:20:40.410
we gotta see exactly
