00:20:40.410 --> 00:20:42.090
From there, we
have to figure out

00:20:42.090 --> 00:20:45.690
what comes in every year or
every month, and what goes out.

00:20:45.690 --> 00:20:46.714
And let me explain.

00:20:46.714 --> 00:20:48.380
So I can't tell you
the number of people

00:20:48.380 --> 00:20:50.480
that are like, I make $100,000.

