Because you have to think of
your life in after tax dollars.

00:20:56.466 --> 00:20:58.090
And the reason why
we say that is, one,

00:20:58.090 --> 00:21:01.600
it's really easy to over inflate
what your household income is.

00:21:01.600 --> 00:21:05.280
Like, you make $100,000, I make
$200,000, we make $300,000.

00:21:05.280 --> 00:21:08.070
But you have to think
about an after tax dollars.

00:21:08.070 --> 00:21:10.120
So first, look at
your paychecks.

00:21:10.120 --> 00:21:12.740
Quickly figure out,
multiply it by 26 or 27,

00:21:12.740 --> 00:21:14.922
based on the number
